    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "BRANIFF\nSCHEDULES\nEFFECTIVE\nSEPTEMBER 1\n1980\nBraniff International",
      "NEW SERVICE\nHIGHLIGHTS\nEUROPE\n• From Dallas-Fort Worth, the only service to\nLondon's convenient Gatwick Airport, all\n747s, everyday, plus the only 747 thru-plane\nservice to Amsterdam, Brussels and Frankfurt.\n• From Boston, Braniff has the only non-stop\n747 service to all of these European cities -\nAmstersdam, Brussels, Frankfurt and Paris'\nclose-in Orly Airport.\nFAR EAST/\nPACIFIC\n•Seom, a 475 the mo 15 to\nHong Kong and Guam.\n• Business Class Service on every flight.\nSOUTH\nAMERICA\n• From New York's JFK Airport, Braniff offers\nthe only non-stop service to Panama plus\nnon stops to Buenos Aires and Guayaquil.\n• From Miami, Braniff flies non-stop to Rio de\nJaneiro, Buenos Aires, Bogota, Guayaquil,\nLima, Panama and Quito.\n• From Los Angeles and San Francisco, Branift\nhas the only thru service to Sao Paulo,\ncontinuing on to Rio. Plus non-stops to\nBogota, Lima and Santiago from Los Angeles;\nthru from San Francisco.\n• From New Orleans, Braniff has the only non-\nstop service to Maracaibo and Panama and the\nonly thru service to Caracas.\nWe better be better.\nWere\nBrariff\nMainland U.S.A., Hawaii, Canada, The Pacific, Mexico,\nSouth America, Britain, Europe, Asia,",
      "Hong Kong\n• Fairbanks\nSeattle/Tacoma\n• Calgary\nAnchorage\nPortland •\nMinneapolis St. Paul\nAlbany\nBoston\nMilwaukee\nDetroit\ncleveland\nReno\nSalt Lake City\nDes Moines\nOmaha\nHartford\nNew York\nNewark\nPhiladelphia\n• Washington\nDenver\nSan Francisco\nLas\nVegas\nColorado\nSprings\nKansas City\nWichita\nLos Angeles\nOklahoma\nCity\nMemphis\n• Nashville\n• Phoenix\nTucson •\nAmarillo\nLubbock\nMidland/Odessa\nDallas-Fort Worth\nAtlanta\n• Jacksonville\nAustin\nSan Antonio\nHonolulu\nHouston\n• Corpus Christi\n• Brownsville\nNew\nOrleans\nTampa\nSt. Petersburg\nClearwater\n• Orlando\nWest Palm Beach\nFt. Lauderdale\nMiami\nU.S. Mainland\nHawaii\nCanada\nAlaska\nBRANIFF INTERNATIONAL\nBoston\nNew York\nWashington, D.C\nLondon\nAmsterdam\nBesses\n• Frankfurt\nSan Francisco\nParis\nSeoul\nLos Angeles\nDallas-Fort Worth\nHouston\nNew\nSan Antonio\nOrleans\nAcaouico a Mexico City\nHonolulu\nMaracaibo\n• Caracas\nBogotá\nGateways For\nAsia\nEurope\nMiddle East\nGuam\nTransatlantic\nTranspacific\nMexico\nSouth America\nGuayaquil\nManaus\nLima\nLa Paz\nSão\n• Paulo®\n→ Rio de Janeiro\nSantiago\n• Buenos Aires"
